{"type": "article", "id": 13708, "title": "浴室收纳架", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-19T07:36:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122446EOGdmna8LCWDIUX3.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t墨尔本设计工作室 Groupwork 推出了一款名为 “Simplify” 的浴室收纳架，包括毛巾悬挂处，肥皂托盘，小物件收纳盒，牙刷和刷子放置处，以及纸巾悬挂处。和它的名字一样，产品的设计非常简单明晰，但在细节上非常充实和体贴，考虑到浴室各种常见的物品，并集中在简洁的一条横梁之上。同时，金色和木质棕色的搭配看上和谐而明快，是件能给沐浴带来好心情的产品。产品可以组合使用，也可以拆分来依照需求购买。<a href=\"http://www.groupworkstudio.com/#intro\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141411G5aMJwkKALNOmyYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141412uhvgEJGrUcwNy205.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141412SLOkAvwRbGrKz0Mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141413bIK4GvJWFuXj9ghx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141413PK4q79DJv8klBa1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141413AP7uMIDx8wvlms0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414149wDOVZQnpY4yu1Bt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}